{"tid":1574219,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被指串謀毀輕鐵設施　三被告獲准保釋　須禁足輕鐵港鐵","createTime":"2019-09-16T10:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T10:31:31.000Z","uid":68738,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"62126344704d44a2ae83fc55155ec98af86c18b6","tid":1574219,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T10:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/67599559_10158621605928998_1382792191558025216_o_zSasO_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F67599559_10158621605928998_1382792191558025216_o_zSasO_1200x0.png&h=7f010e40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方 9 月 5 日凌晨於屯門截查一架可以車輛，並從車上搜出鎚仔、螺絲批等物品，車上 3 名男子被指圖謀破壞輕鐵站出入閘感應器，被控一項串謀損壞財產罪。三人本月 7 日首次提堂後被還押，三人今日（16日）再向高等法院申請保釋。高等法院批准三人以 2 萬元現金及 2 萬元人事擔保，但須遵守宵禁令、每日向指定警署報到、禁足所有輕鐵及港鐵站、不得離開香港及交出旅遊證件等條件。<br />\n<br />\n三名被告分別為李懷恩（23歲）、張溱煒（24歲）及李鈞浩（24歲）。控罪指，三人涉嫌今年 9 月 5 日在屯門青山魚類批發市場外，與他人串謀損壞港鐵財產，即輕鐵站的出入閘感應器、售票機和閉路電視鏡頭。案件將於11月27日再訊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%B2%E8%AC%80%E6%AF%80%E8%BC%95%E9%90%B5%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD-%E4%B8%89%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E7%8D%B2%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B-%E9%A0%88%E7%A6%81%E8%B6%B3%E8%BC%95%E9%90%B5%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E4%25B8%25B2%25E8%25AC%2580%25E6%25AF%2580%25E8%25BC%2595%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%2596%25BD-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B-%25E9%25A0%2588%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E8%25BC%2595%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%2F&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbeTO5ApsLFANoEfWU0iq%2Bkc%3D&h=0c082b9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E4%25B8%25B2%25E8%25AC%2580%25E6%25AF%2580%25E8%25BC%2595%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%2